Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_rx_tx_status

AGL_GMX_RX_TX_STATUS = GMX RX/TX Status

Notes: RX[0], TX[0] will be reset when MIX0_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. RX[1], TX[1] will be reset when MIX1_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
